      <hr class="my-5">            <div id="chapter-id-26420" class="paragraph paragraph--type--chapter paragraph--view-mode--default">
          
          <h2 class="field__label">Vertically Integrated Projects (VIP)</h2>
    
      <div class="field field--name-field-structured-body field--type-entity-reference-revisions field--label-hidden field__items">
              <div class="field__item">  <div class="paragraph paragraph--type--styled-text paragraph--view-mode--default">
          
            <div class="clearfix text-formatted field field--name-field-styled-text field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field__item"><p>The Vertically Integrated Projects (VIP) program provides a multi-year, integrated approach to learning that emphasizes <strong>project-based, interdisciplinary, research-active education</strong>. It provides an opportunity to learn and practice professional skills while making real-world contributions.</p>
<ul>
</ul>
</div>
      
      </div>
</div>
              <div class="field__item">



  <div class="paragraph paragraph--type--call-to-action paragraph--view-mode--default">

    
      <div class="row">

