              <div class="field__item">  <div class="paragraph paragraph--type--styled-text paragraph--view-mode--default">
          
            <div class="clearfix text-formatted field field--name-field-styled-text field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field__item"><ul>
</ul>
<h3>Additional Opportunities</h3>
<p>Numerous STEM research programs open to undergraduate students are available throughout the country. Search for programs by discipline or geography using <a href="http://www.pathwaystoscience.org/Programs.aspx">Pathways to Science</a>. Listed below are a few select programs:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.nsf.gov/funding/pgm_summ.jsp?pims_id=5517">Research Experiences for Undergraduates (REU)</a>&nbsp;- National Science Foundation</li>
<li><a href="https://science.osti.gov/wdts/suli">Science Undergraduate Laboratory Internship</a>&nbsp;- US Department of Energy</li>
<li><a href="http://www.nist.gov/surf/">Summer Undergraduate Research Fellowship (SURF)</a> - National Institute of Standards and Technology </li>
<li><a href="http://www.fhwa.dot.gov/tpp/ddetfp.htm">Dwight David Eisenhower Transportation Fellowship Program</a> - US Department of Transportation</li>
</ul>
<p><strong><a href="http://engineering.nyu.edu/research-innovation/student-research/international-opportunities">International Opportunities</a></strong></p>
</div>
      
      </div>
</div>
          </div>
  
      </div>

      <hr class="my-5">            <div id="chapter-id-26424" class="paragraph paragraph--type--chapter paragraph--view-mode--default">
          
          <h2 class="field__label">Graduate Research </h2>
    
      <div class="field field--name-field-structured-body field--type-entity-reference-revisions field--label-hidden field__items">
              <div class="field__item">  <div class="paragraph paragraph--type--styled-text paragraph--view-mode--default">
          
            <div class="clearfix text-formatted field field--name-field-styled-text field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field__item"><h4>NYU Resources</h4>
<ul>
<li>Both the <a href="http://engineering.nyu.edu/office-sponsored-programs">School of Engineering's Office of Sponsored Programs</a> and <a href="https://www.nyu.edu/research/resources-and-support-offices/getting-started-withyourresearch/office-of-sponsored-programs.html">NYU's Office of Sponsored Programs</a> provide information about research funding opportunities. </li>
</ul>
<h4>Transformative Summer Research Experience (TREx) for Masters Students</h4>
<p>The Transformative Research Experience (TREx) is a selective 10-week program exclusively for new incoming masters students seeking to contribute to impactful research. Taking place in Summer between your first and second years, TREx offers a unique opportunity to engage in hands-on research under the guidance of our faculty in critical fields such as sustainability, systems engineering, cybersecurity, wireless, AI, robotics, and more. Applications for newly admitted Fall 2026 students are now open, on an invite-only basis.</p>
<h4>Fellowship Opportunities in STEM </h4>
<p>Explore our list of <a href="https://engineering.nyu.edu/academics/graduate/phd-hub/fellowships">Fellowship Opportunities</a>.</p>
<p>Search for programs by discipline or geography using <a href="http://www.pathwaystoscience.org/">Pathways to Science</a>. Listed below are a few select programs:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.nsf.gov/funding/pgm_summ.jsp?pims_id=6201">Graduate Research Fellowship Program</a>&nbsp;- National Science Foundation</li>
<li><a href="http://www.krellinst.org/csgf/">DOE Computational Science Graduate Fellowship</a>&nbsp;- US Dept of Energy</li>
<li><a href="https://ndseg.sysplus.com/">National Defense Science and Engineering Graduate (NDSEG) Fellowship</a> - US Dept of Defense</li>
<li><a href="https://intern.nasa.gov/">NASA Internships and Fellowships</a></li>
<li><a href="https://researchtraining.nih.gov/programs/fellowships?CFID=66155710&amp;CFTOKEN=de81a6facc4760fb-C576DB8A-5056-9439-7E2EBF6845556C91">National Institutes of Health</a></li>
<li><a href="https://science.osti.gov/wdts/scgsr">Office of Science Graduate Student Research (SCGSR)</a> - US Dept of Energy</li>
<li><a href="http://www.fhwa.dot.gov/tpp/ddetfp.htm">Dwight David Eisenhower Transportation Graduate Fellowship </a>- US Department of Transportation</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>International Summer Research: </strong><a href="/research-innovation/student-research/international-opportunities#chapter-id-17013">Practical Research Experience Program (PREP) at the Technical University of Munich (TUM)</a><br>Graduate students can apply for a 10-week summer program in Germany.</p>
</div>
      
      </div>
</div>
          </div>
  
      </div>

      <hr class="my-5">            <div id="chapter-id-35716" class="paragraph paragraph--type--chapter paragraph--view-mode--default">
          
          <h2 class="field__label">Research Excellence Exhibit</h2>
    
      <div class="field field--name-field-structured-body field--type-entity-reference-revisions field--label-hidden field__items">
              <div class="field__item">  <div class="paragraph paragraph--type--styled-text paragraph--view-mode--default">
          
            <div class="clearfix text-formatted field field--name-field-styled-text field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field__item"><p>The Research Excellence Exhibit is an annual public event at NYU Tandon which features exhibits that illustrate the scope of engineering and the applied sciences — and their potential for improving the world. Find out more and see lists of past projects at our <a href="https://engineering.nyu.edu/research/student-research/research-expo">Research Excellence Exhibit</a> page.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
</div>
      
